ase the known spectral complexity of active galactic nuclei and\nshould further stimulate a combined theoretical and observational effort to\nachieve a better understanding of the physics of the innermost regions of AGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 May 2003 06:59:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
